<m0>Wheels spinning over contro<m2><ql>
<ql>
ntro<m0>l of six Dade toll roads<ql>
<m1><ue5><m2><ql>
<m4>   LINE 1 IS .75 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS 1.152 INCHES<m2><ql>
